### 2e. Missing required field (no debitAccount) — expect 400 validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
