### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 8. TRIGGER DEBIT
###    Manually triggers a debit for a failed subscription.
###    Uses referenceNo (not subscriptionId) to look up the record.
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 8a. Trigger — happy path (will fire transaction callback asynchronously)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/trigger-debit
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "referenceId": "REF_2026_001",
  "productId": "{{productId}}"
}

###

### 8b. Trigger — reference not found
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/trigger-debit
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "referenceId": "REF_DOES_NOT_EXIST",
  "productId": "{{productId}}"
}


### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 9. SCHEDULE ONE-TIME DEBIT
###    Schedules a single future debit. debitDate must be 24+ hours away.
###    callbackUrl here is a per-request fallback (provision URL takes priority).
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 9a. Schedule — happy path (success scenario, account ends 001)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/schedule-debit
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "country": "{{country}}",
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "debitAmount": "150.00",
  "debitDate": "2026-06-15",
  "debitTime": "14:30",
  "debitNotificationAccount": "0241234001",
  "referenceNo": "REF_SCHED_001",
  "channel": "MTN",
  "currency": "GHS",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}"
}

###

### 9b. Schedule — debitDate is today (less than 24h away) — expect responseCode 100
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/schedule-debit
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "country": "{{country}}",
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "debitAmount": "150.00",
  "debitDate": "2026-05-07",
  "debitTime": "10:00",
  "referenceNo": "REF_SCHED_002",
  "channel": "MTN",
  "currency": "GHS",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}"
}


